## Summary
Refiner (Cohort) integration allows Amplitude users to sync cohorts to Refiner for targeted user feedback collection, requiring a paid Refiner plan and Amplitude plan. The setup involves copying API Key and Segment ID from Refiner settings and configuring the destination in Amplitude's Catalog.

